a One page multipurpose wordpress theme

Intro

"Osman" is a WordPress theme, packed with nice features like Page Onepage with ready onepage menu, pushmenu,slider sidebar, custom post types, widgetized sidebars and footers, custom meta boxes and a beautiful admin panel. Inside the admin panel, which is located in wp-admin->Osman Options, you`ll be able to customize the theme without the need of touching a single line of code.

Installation

After unzipped the downloaded package from Themeforest. Now, in the extracted package you will find a folder named "Osman Theme" and 2 archives: "osman.zip" file and "osmanchild.zip" which are the archives for the wordpress theme and child theme of Osman. 

If you plan to edit the theme files, like style.css, I`m suggesting you to install both Osman and Osman Child themes, then activate the child theme. Child themes are great because allow you to edit the theme and also lets you update the original theme in the future, without loosing your edited files work. 

Read more about child themes and how to use them here: http://codex.wordpress.org/Child_Themes

You can install the themes in two ways:

  • FTP: Extract "osman.zip" file and upload the "patti" folder to /wp-content/themes/ folder on your server. If you want to use the child theme for future theme editing, extract "osman-child.zip" file and upload "osman-child" folder to /wp-content/themes/ folder on your server too. 
  • WordPress: Navigate to Appearance -> Themes -> Add New -> Upload page. Select osman.zip file. Press the Install Now button to upload and install the theme. Then do the same for the child theme as well, if you plan to use the child theme.

After uploading the theme, you have to activate it. Navigate to Appearence -> Themes page to activate the theme.

Plugins

In order to get the most out of a website, the theme is packed with a series of WordPress plugins: 

1 - Osman Core - is a  plugin built especially for Osman which makes the theme work at its maximum capability(admin options, shortcodes, custom post types) . 

2. Price Tables - Osman Theme shortcode have price table shortcode but you can use it for me variations.

3. Contact Form 7 - osman theme have contact form shortcode but you can use it for more options. 

4. Breadcrumb NavXT- osman theme have own build-in breadcrum but you can use this plugin. 

5. WooCommerce - is a plugin can support osman. 

6. Menu Swapper - is a plugin use for multiple menu location replace specially for one page.

 

 

After installing the theme, you`ll see a box message telling you about the plugins, which one is recommended and which one is required.

Install the plugins and activate them.

If you feel that they`re not installed properly, go to Appearance->Install Plugins and make sure that the list is empty.

Using Demo Content

Go to Wp-admin->Osman Options->Demo Importer, you get demo contents with images. Just click on any demo contents. After some time it's all you find into wp-admin->pages. Like after install one page demo you get one page menu check for default. You can browse the page like ../onepage

After finish import demo content then goto Wp-admin->appearance->Menus

just check menu checked with it's corresponding pages.

Page Pre-loader

You can active page pre-loader from wp-admin->osman options->page preloader, also can style it.

Pages

To create WordPress pages, go to Pages->Add New. After enter new page you can get Icon name OT into visual window. You can select shortcodes from this. You can also Choose you page options from page settings.

 

 

OnePage

For one page creation, Create a page with selected template one page. It's located after publish button name page atributes.

After save that page, you create the pages what you want to under this page show as single page. After create that pages you have to enable the options "One Page Include" into page settings. After enbale one page for this page then select in which page should show that page with the options "Which one page template include the current page" located page settings below.

 you can set order that set priority. low priority show the page first. you Can get it after page template.

after create and select all pages now you goto menu from wp-admin->appreance->menus

After create menu name, you get menu pages from left pages sidebar. All pages add into Menu Structure and select one page menu location from menu settings  save them. Now you get ready your one page.

 

Multiple one page

Repeat one page section with another pages. After that from Menu Swapper plugin you can create another menu location from wp-admin->settings->menu swapper

Now you can create another menu name after that assign this menu location with the menu name where you add selected pages.

After creating menu location,assign menu name to that location. we goto that page where we added the pages. The another one page should select the onepage template.

Now you can browse another one page with same theme but different menu.

 

Blog Posts

Blog posts are the items of a blog. You can create them from Posts->Add New. 

There are several types of blog post types, based on a number of post formats. osman is making use of 6 post formats, to increase the functionality of your website and make your blog area look like a microblogging website: Standard, Gallery, Link, Quote, Audio and Video. 

 

Each one of them has its own extra options. For example, in Gallery format, you`ll be able to upload images for the gallery, while in Video format, you`ll have the possibility to use a video from a third party website like YouTube or Vimeo. 

I encourage you to "Set a featured Image" for all your blog posts, to enhance your website with images and make it more user friendly.

You can change blog layout from admin options.

Also can change single post layout

Also can change author box.

Author social share get from wp-admin-users->your profile

You can change blog typography from osman options->typography

Page as home page

You can choose page or post as home page from wp-admin->settings->reading

 

custom post type

You can change layout and  can add remove custom post type from osman options custom post type section.

Slider

wp-admin->carousel->add new click and write name as home and save, after you can upload images and add captions.

After save name you can uplaod images, you can use html into caption. you can set feature image for only into show admin.

you can get shortcode from carousel.

You can select slider into page settings. At first choose slider alias type after that slider alias from select box.

Portfolio

You can add portfolio from wp-admin->portfolio->add new, You can use shortcodes into portfolio. You can use video into portfolio. You can add categories from wp-admin->portfolio-> portfolio categories.

You can change portfolio slug from wp-admin->osman options->custome post type->portfolio

Team

You can add team from wp-admin->team and can show with shortcodes.

You can control and change slug from wp-admin->osman options->custom post types->team

 

partner

You can add partner from wp-admin->partner.

You can control partner from wp-admin->osman options-.custom post types.

Widgets

To manage widgets, go to Appearance->Widgets

Osman has 7 widgetized areas (default sidebar, Blog Sidebar, Footer, Page Sidebar,woocommerce sidebar, pushmenu top and pushmenu bottom sidebar).

Osman comes with 7 custom widgets:

  • Osman: Twitter: Adds a twitter feed from a twitter account.Make sure that you create a twitter app, because you`ll need some authentication details in order to use the widget. Go to https://dev.twitter.com/apps to create a twitter app.
  • Osman: Flickr: Adds a feed of images from a Flickr ID.
  • Osman: Recent Posts slider: Displays recent posts on your site. Is ideally to be used on Blog Sidebar.
  • Osman: facebook like box: Facebook Like Box
  • Osman - Google+ Badge Box: Google+ Badge Box

Sidebar

You can active add content into sidebar widget from wp-admin->appreance->widgets

You can also change sidebar design from wp-admin->osman options->sidebar

You can change sidebar typography from wp-admin->osman options->typography->sidebar

Floating Sidebar

You can on floating sidebar from wp-admin->osman options->floating sidebar

 

Woocommerce

After acrive woocommerce you can style it from osman options->woocommerce

Comming /Maintenance

You can enable comming soon page from wp-admin->osman options ->maintenance mode. Only non-users can show this.
